<br>
Yes yes, I know that's the way the game should be.  But the fact is they're trying to drag as many monthly subscriptions as they can for as long as they can.  This move buys them a larger amount of people who now think they have a chance at getting at some of the higher content.  <br>
<br>
Pure business move.<br>
<br>
It should come as no surprise to anyone though, it's really the same sort of thing they've been doing forever.  Being part of a &quot;top&quot; guild isn't going to entitle you to anything but getting a jump on everyone else.  You have to know by now eventually the doors will be flung wide open and the mob will rush in. <p>-Tain<BR>
